==English==
===Etymology===
{{compound|en|yellow|knife|gloss1=a colour like that of copper|gloss2=a tool prominently made, used, owned, and traded, by the T'satsąot'ınę}}.
From {{der|en|dgr|T'satsąot'ınę}}.
Named after the {{m|en|Tsatsaotine|gloss=Copper People}} {{gloss|the {{w|lang=en|Yellowknives}}}}, a local {{l|en|Dene}} tribe that made {{l|en|copper}} tools.
